text: Jordyn, better known as "Jordy", is Kylie's best friend. In fact, they're basically attached at the hip and often refer to each other as "wife." Jordyn is making her name known in the modeling world, and also seems to be Kylie's guiding light at times. She says there's a lot of pressure being the best friend of someone who is constantly in the spotlight — but for her, it's worth it.3.2 millionpursuing her own career in fashion and modeling. In March of 2016, Woods told Refinery29 that she loves being a positive role model in the modeling world. "The fact that I can be considered a model and not be a size zero is awesome," she said. "I even get comments on my Instagram saying things like, ‘If she can be a model, I can be a model’ — and that’s true."
